// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0154 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: ff2fbe5a-7485-5b04-831f-a350e490493f

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
